{"analytics_identifier":null,"base_path":"/government/organisations/office-for-zero-emission-vehicles/about/research","content_id":"8c94d5dd-688f-4b2f-ab28-41678abf1864","description":"Supporting emerging technologies which the UK can exploit and lead globally, where full commercial funding is not otherwise available.\r\n","details":{"attachments":[],"body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>Supporting innovation to put the <abbr title=\"United Kingdom\">UK</abbr> at the forefront of the design, manufacture and use of zero emission vehicles.</p>\n\n<p>The Office for Zero Emission Vehicles (<abbr title=\"Office for Zero Emission Vehicles\">OZEV</abbr>) funds and manages a programme of industry-led research and development to support emerging technologies to capture the environmental and economic benefits of the transition for the <abbr title=\"United Kingdom\">UK</abbr>.</p>\n\n<p>The government is committed to accelerating the pace of change in zero emission vehicle (<abbr title=\"Zero Emission Vehicle\">ZEV</abbr>) technology and contributes to the funding of a range of innovative research and development activities.\n<abbr title=\"Office for Zero Emission Vehicles\">OZEV</abbr> is focused on identifying and supporting emerging technologies in both the vehicles and their infrastructure to:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>support growth of the <abbr title=\"United Kingdom\">UK</abbr>’s automotive, <abbr title=\"Zero Emission Vehicle\">ZEV</abbr> infrastructure and energy sectors</li>\n  <li>increase and accelerate the introduction of zero emission vehicles by addressing challenges and barriers</li>\n  <li>help the <abbr title=\"United Kingdom\">UK</abbr> reduce CO2 and other emissions caused by road transport</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>We set competitions to fund collaborative research and development. The scope and criteria is created with input from a wide range of stakeholders. Project bids are assessed independently by a panel of industry experts and are required to be co-funded by the private sector.</p>\n\n</div>","change_history":[{"note":"First published.","public_timestamp":"2020-12-07T17:09:12Z"}],"organisation":"57f7737a-90e3-4e24-9de1-b4312830b4e7","tags":{"browse_pages":[]}},"document_type":"research","first_published_at":"2020-12-07T17:09:12+00:00","links":{"available_translations":[{"api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/office-for-zero-emission-vehicles/about/research","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/office-for-zero-emission-vehicles/about/research","base_path":"/government/organisations/office-for-zero-emission-vehicles/about/research","content_id":"8c94d5dd-688f-4b2f-ab28-41678abf1864","document_type":"research","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2020-12-07T17:09:12Z","schema_name":"corporate_information_page","title":"Research at OZEV","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/office-for-zero-emission-vehicles/about/research","withdrawn":false}],"organisations":[{"analytics_identifier":"OT1323","api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/office-for-zero-emission-vehicles","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/office-for-zero-emission-vehicles","base_path":"/government/organisations/office-for-zero-emission-vehicles","content_id":"57f7737a-90e3-4e24-9de1-b4312830b4e7","details":{"acronym":"OZEV","brand":"department-for-transport","default_news_image":null,"logo":{"crest":"single-identity","formatted_title":"Office for Zero Emission Vehicles"},"organisation_govuk_status":{"status":"live","updated_at":null,"url":null}},"document_type":"organisation","links":{},"locale":"en","schema_name":"organisation","title":"Office for Zero Emission Vehicles","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/office-for-zero-emission-vehicles","withdrawn":false}],"taxons":[{"api_path":"/api/content/transport/driving-and-road-transport","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/transport/driving-and-road-transport","base_path":"/transport/driving-